title: U.S. will not directly confront Russia in Syria, Obama says
text:
05 U.S. will not directly confront Russia in Syria, Obama says 
The Washington Post: President Obama has decided not to directly confront Russia over its new air offensive in Syria, believing that President Vladi­mir Putin will soon find himself in a Syrian “quagmire,” but he has approved a new escalation of U.S. efforts against the Islamic State.
